"Injiza Umumaro ( &ie; , A Umumaro in i Ifishi %S: Y = F ( x ) ) &kmplot; , "
"Injiza in i Ifishi %S: : <screen> \n"
"<userinput> <replaceable> F </replaceable> ( <replaceable> x </"
"replaceable> ) = <replaceable> imvugo </replaceable> </userinput> \n"
"</screen> : "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>f</replaceable> is the name of the function, and can be any "
