"Uburyo . Bya i Umigereka Bihari ya:  Imimaro na [ A , b ] Akazi ya:  "
"Imimaro . Urugero: : <screen> \n"
"<userinput> \n"
"F ( x ) = x ^ 2 ; </userinput> \n"
"</screen> Herekana %S i Y = x <superscript> 2 </superscript> Na: Itangira . "
