#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The caret symbol performs exponentiation. &eg;, <userinput>2^4</userinput> "
"returns 16."
msgstr "IKIMENYETSO . &eg; , <userinput> 2 ^ 4 </userinput> 16 . "

#. Tag: term
